QuestData.Title: Journey into Thunder Bluff
QuestData.Description: You will now be revered within our great city. Any $r worthy of completing the Rites of the Earthmother earns that honor.$b$bFor your final quest, seek out our young leader, Baine Bloodhoof, who dwells atop the highest mesa in Thunder Bluff.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Baine Bloodhoof in Thunder Bluff.
